[1.144, "o", "========================================================================\r\n"]
[0.002, "o", "Building OS-dependent module\r\n"]
[0.003, "o", "If you get No such file error messages for files x509.h, ssl.h,\r\n"]
[0.002, "o", "pem.h, buffer.h, bio.h, and crypto.h, that means that OpenSSL\r\n"]
[0.003, "o", "is not installed on your system. Either install OpenSSL first\r\n"]
[0.007, "o", "or build with command: make slx SSLTYPE=none\r\n"]
[0.003, "o", "========================================================================\r\n"]
