[0.004, "o", "\u001b[?25l\u001b[48;160H   \u001b[H; (time to live) Sets the number of second while cached file will be used\u001b[2;3Hinstead of original one.\u001b[41X\u001b[3;3Hhttps://php.net/soap.wsdl-cache-ttl\u001b[20X\r\nsoap.wsdl_cache_ttl=86400\u001b[5X\u001b[6;3HSets the size of the cache limit. (Max. number of WSDL files to cache)   \r\nsoap.wsdl_cache_limit = 5\u001b[49X\r\n\u001b[46X\n\u001b[96m[sysvshm]\u001b[m\u000f\u001b[17X\r\n; A default size of the shared memory segment\u001b[11;2Hsysvshm.init_mem = 10000\u001b[37X\r\n\u001b[26X\n\u001b[96m[ldap]\u001b[14;3H\u001b[m\u000fSets the maximum number of open links or -1 for unlimited.\u001b[14X\r\nldap.max_links =\u001b[92m -1\u001b[m\u000f\u001b[10X\r\n\u001b[24X\n\u001b[96m[dba]\u001b[18;2H\u001b[m\u000fdba.default_handler=\u001b[55X\r\n\u001b[79X\n\u001b[96m[opcache]\u001b[m\u000f\u001b[53X\u001b[21;2H Determines if Zend OPCache is enabled\r\n;opcache.enable=1\r\n\u001b[72X\u001b[24;2H Determines if Zend OPCache is enabled for the CLI version of PHP\r\n;opcache.enable_cli=0\r\n\u001b[71X\u001b[27;3HThe OPcache shared memory storage size.\u001b[28;10Hmemory_consumption=128\u001b[7X\u001b[30;2H The amount of memory for interned strings in Mbytes.\r\n;opcache.interned_strings_buffer=8\r\n\u001b[65X\u001b[33;3HThe maximum number of keys (scripts) in the OPcache hash table.\u001b[9X\u001b[34;3HOnly numbers between 200 and 1000000 are allowed.\u001b[22X\u001b[35;2Hopcache.max_accelerated_files=10000\u001b[34X\r\n\u001b[73X\u001b[37;3HThe maximum percentage of \"wasted\" memory until a restart is scheduled.\u001b[38;10Hmax_wasted_percentage=5\u001b[40;3HWhen this directive is enabled, the OPcache appends the current working\u001b[41;3Hdirectory to the script key, thus eliminating possible collisions between\u001b[42;2H files with the same name (basename). Disabling the directive improves\r\n; performance, but may break existing applications.\u001b[44;2Hopcache.use_cwd=1\u001b[59X\r\n\u001b[24X\u001b[46;2H When disabled, you must reset the OPcache manually or restart the\u001b[47;154H\u001b[0;10;7m\u000f698,13        90\u001b[46;13H\u001b[?25h"]
